spans.text: Wit they called the shining dame
Wit they called the shining dame
Was valued as a gift from wit
The different value each should share , And in the eye of reason bear
scarce a feature , Which was not copied from ill-nature
every weakness he displayed , His errors
If aught is in my origin , Of either pure or breath divine
appear , O ! save me from my dreaded foe , Who plans my kingdom's overthrow
The subtle essence of thy power
thy reign , Then all inspiring thou shalt move Judgement , thy native charms to love
by his creative power , A brighter world within
